{"tid":2302092,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"想問大家真係準備好反抗未？","createTime":"2020-11-27T00:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T00:52:08.000Z","uid":205928,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e36f68ff7bba7e9c49bc175548699906b42806d7","tid":2302092,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:49:08.000Z","msg":"ONE REELER概念照已經睇到晒<br />\n信和爆碟 同站姐換卡仔 隨時準備黎料<br />\n依家已經話要眾籌幫學生買專輯<br />\n<br />\n一開始就係唔反空降車汪/閪女人柔嘅話就唔俾入音樂台<br />\n 根住就娛台/ tg谷<br />\n個個都逆來順受/唔理就滲入每個生活細節<br />\n依家既反抗已經唔係話下下要娛台出po吹奏<br />\n而係細至你睇po唔正皮要解散izone既cm<br />\n唔負皮wizone手足<br />\n如果個個都肯咁做 先可以阻止489/路人黑得寸進尺<br />\n雖然我覺得大家都會無所謂照過日常生活"},{"pid":"e7ed066027cbe0bd71abf12e6a2409ef8fdcf491","tid":2302092,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f53a656a2b5c848ea64285ae1818970c8e8f4c","tid":2302092,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c61e9e8593886824c21b8e097b0ed4bbacaa464","tid":2302092,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2640fe02696a89ddc50dd958019eda72520b8b","tid":2302092,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:52:08.000Z","msg":"準時返工啦柒頭"}]}